{"tid":672004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有錢人做馬會會員都麻煩d 要人介紹先得","createTime":"2018-05-20T15:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T16:18:25.000Z","uid":63202,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0a06b2b3fb95ecc03f5df06b3226a28e54e2a026","tid":672004,"uid":63202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T15:16:24.000Z","msg":"我落是但一間馬會都做到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a603f3745d33701c09be5e428bbec1fdf30b831c","tid":672004,"uid":52221,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T15:35:32.000Z","msg":"人哋個個係養馬會<br />\n你個個就賭馬會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74fc8b3866b981a520cc2007dd2d06a2141b3421","tid":672004,"uid":63202,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"a603f3745d33701c09be5e428bbec1fdf30b831c","tid":672004,"uid":52221,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T15:35:32.000Z","msg":"人哋個個係養馬會<br />\n你個個就賭馬會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T18:41:36.000Z","msg":"？乜鳩"},{"pid":"2e429d57395acc9065972d89feb8fb23ec6e8c83","tid":672004,"uid":140737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T18:49:15.000Z","msg":"樓主有嘅係人脈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ded606b8c2529f1fdf6c96b355f4416ebb8916a","tid":672004,"uid":85461,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T20:46:44.000Z","msg":"年滿十八歲之人仕都可申請成為賽馬會會員。<br />\n<br />\n擬申請賽馬會員會籍之人仕，必須由本會一位定居香港之名譽董事、名譽遴選會員或遴選會員提名，並獲另一位定居香港之名譽董事、名譽遴選會員或遴選會員附議。另外，申請人亦須列舉三位準備支持其入會申請之本會會員。<br />\n<br />\n若申請成為全費會員，請填妥上述之賽馬會員會籍申請表及全費會員會籍申請表，然後將兩份表格一併交回本會。全費會員會籍申請表可向定居香港之名譽董事、名譽遴選會員(O) 或遴選會員索取。<br />\n<br />\n本會有二百位遴選會員。最新之遴選會員名單可隨時向本會會員事務部索取。<br />\n<br />\n本會董事局有絕對酌情權決定會籍申請成功與否。申請人應仔細參閱相關會籍申請表內的申請條款。"},{"pid":"890dabd550c787ff1e24c7bab7a136cbd3438926","tid":672004,"uid":52221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74fc8b3866b981a520cc2007dd2d06a2141b3421","tid":672004,"uid":63202,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"a603f3745d33701c09be5e428bbec1fdf30b831c","tid":672004,"uid":52221,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T15:35:32.000Z","msg":"人哋個個係養馬會<br />\n你個個就賭馬會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T18:41:36.000Z","msg":"？乜鳩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:23:20.000Z","msg":"唔撚識睇字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e740d3732866d17e9c48ef10bafa3802a7c3a0d","tid":672004,"uid":164991,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:42:37.000Z","msg":"其實馬會member有分好多種<br />\n<br />\n如果後生仔30歲前可以入Racing Club (競駿會) ,會費有discount, 好似6萬左右入(而家唔知加左幾多錢),之後再俾月費<br />\n有興趣入可以上番racing club個網有form填之後會有馬會manager聯絡你傾計<br />\n或者join馬會d event, 入去食飯, 同d manager傾計,等佢地多d聯絡你<br />\n<br />\n當你入左racing club, 同d member / manager 混熟左,佢地就會慢慢介紹d voting member / full member你識, 到時睇下你想唔想做racing member (12萬8)/ full member (40萬) (唔知加左幾多價) ....<br />\n<br />\n最後就係同D VOTING / OWNER 熟...爭取睇下有冇機會入到佢地D GROUP, 玩團體馬 / 入籤抽馬 做馬主"},{"pid":"c2ea73a41e68b6f77e689eba8795ed09bc8fcbca","tid":672004,"uid":63202,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"890dabd550c787ff1e24c7bab7a136cbd3438926","tid":672004,"uid":52221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74fc8b3866b981a520cc2007dd2d06a2141b3421","tid":672004,"uid":63202,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"a603f3745d33701c09be5e428bbec1fdf30b831c","tid":672004,"uid":52221,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T15:35:32.000Z","msg":"人哋個個係養馬會<br />\n你個個就賭馬會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T18:41:36.000Z","msg":"？乜鳩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:23:20.000Z","msg":"唔撚識睇字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:46:08.000Z","msg":"睇乜鳩"},{"pid":"65cdb1fc6ea7f08a38e72be7dbda2352a5c870a3","tid":672004,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:49:16.000Z","msg":"其實大部份會所會員都要有人介紹先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05fa47893cd4cb5c10bccbe0743cd8c7f6ca14fe","tid":672004,"uid":63202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"890dabd550c787ff1e24c7bab7a136cbd3438926","tid":672004,"uid":52221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74fc8b3866b981a520cc2007dd2d06a2141b3421","tid":672004,"uid":63202,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"a603f3745d33701c09be5e428bbec1fdf30b831c","tid":672004,"uid":52221,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T15:35:32.000Z","msg":"人哋個個係養馬會<br />\n你個個就賭馬會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T18:41:36.000Z","msg":"？乜鳩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:23:20.000Z","msg":"唔撚識睇字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:43:00.000Z","msg":"你都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"443bca42ac9900b115f9d0dccddb5dee25c08d85","tid":672004,"uid":76747,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"申請左做會員<br />\n掛個章落部車頭落老蘭一轉型能到"},{"pid":"eacfebbc0b37219bbdbb89763fc597bbe74629d9","tid":672004,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:45:02.000Z","msg":"你呢d無人無物<br />\n<br />\n開個ac保持一定投注，入競駿會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d135014281408282e5e48a87c4f295f681afd057","tid":672004,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:03:48.000Z","msg":"我介紹你呀樓主"},{"pid":"5cfeabd163d1c2d198123fb7acfc42ec473f6b28","tid":672004,"uid":164991,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"443bca42ac9900b115f9d0dccddb5dee25c08d85","tid":672004,"uid":76747,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"申請左做會員<br />\n掛個章落部車頭落老蘭一轉型能到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:08:43.000Z","msg":"個章呢....唔係會員都掛得,要睇係睇CAR PARK LABEL <br />\n有章冇CAR PARK..人地就知你扮野..."},{"pid":"c5e496af659ef61ea4a1ae6e2d86e26f76327cdf","tid":672004,"uid":54373,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:16:38.000Z","msg":"其實,做正常會員無可能<br />\n<br />\n自從ICAC查過幾單,無咩鄰選會員肯見你幾面就會同你簽<br />\n<br />\n除非你在上流社會打滾,同3個鄰選會員真相識<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為簽你入個3條友,都要寫信講同你相識幾耐,有咩交情,及點知你係熱愛賽馬"},{"pid":"cada4546a2f81d98eabe4a237a010c2b99152606","tid":672004,"uid":154756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:41:03.000Z","msg":"其實做到正常會員勁唔勁"},{"pid":"7a6553807faad40d13283c568afba1dc15417cc1","tid":672004,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cada4546a2f81d98eabe4a237a010c2b99152606","tid":672004,"uid":154756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:41:03.000Z","msg":"其實做到正常會員勁唔勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:42:51.000Z","msg":"以前入會好亂來,呢5年入會<br />\n真相識先敢簽你<br />\n<br />\n因為幾單ICAC案"},{"pid":"cfc14b109870f0e2ad96e79b9bab8705c375cad3","tid":672